  "instructions": [
    "Fill a small saucepan with 200ml warm water and bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Add the pitted dates and blanch for 2 minutes, then remove and let cool to room temperature.",
    "Segment the orange, removing all pith and membranes.",
    "Juice the lime, reserving some of the zest.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the salad greens, orange segments, cooled dates, toasted pecans, and chopped cilantro.",
    "Whisk together olive oil, maple syrup, apple cider vinegar, lime juice, lime zest, salt, and pepper to create the dressing.",
    "Pour the dressing over the salad and toss gently until all ingredients are evenly coated.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning if necessary.",
    "Divide the salad among four bowls and serve immediately."
  ],
